{"tid":202551,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[KPOP] Mnet《PRODUCE 101 Season 2》討論區(30) 為最討厭的練習生投票！","createTime":"2017-04-15T14:55:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T14:58:33.000Z","uid":1776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d35bb03365d7f796ba8ff3d378ba3c8200c7c967","tid":202551,"uid":1776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:55:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Ed1IkEm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEd1IkEm.jpg&h=4c1138da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/AA9DPJp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAA9DPJp.jpg&h=9e60e63a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/gTwlGuj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgTwlGuj.jpg&h=3e627290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《PRODUCE 101第二季》是Mnet於2017年推出的韓國首個「經紀公司大型企劃男團」新男團選拔／生存實境節目，以101名來自不同經紀公司的男練習生為主角。在節目中，男練習生需要共同生活，接受訓練，以及完成各種不同的任務。國民製作人（觀眾）最終通過投票方式選出11名男練習生，而該11名練習生將會組成限定男團進行活動。第二季國民製作人代表將由BoA擔任。節目暫定於四月七日首播。<br />\n<br />\n投票預告：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/c5-eQyVrJEM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fc5-eQyVrJEM&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=25651c13\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/c5-eQyVrJEM</a><br />\n<br />\nPRODUCE 101第二季預告：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uYeAgiDJ4p0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuYeAgiDJ4p0&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=8f8d2fa8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uYeAgiDJ4p0</a><br />\n <br />\nPRODUCE 101 第二季First Stage 나야나 (PICK ME):<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NIld_iEc67s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNIld_iEc67s&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=55a1ed58\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NIld_iEc67s</a><br />\n<br />\n新手必看花名list：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spr