ime":"2017-04-15T14:56:17.000Z","msg":"Item Support：<br />\n呢個活動每個練習生一日一票<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">當然你可以開好多個分身去投</span></span><br />\n揀你鍾意嘅練習生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n投夠一定票數嘅話 Mnet就會派禮物比你應援嘅練習生<br />\n投票係累積嘅 所以投到某個數目嘅話 Mnet又會送其他野比練習生<br />\n夠100％就會送餐車<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/viruJRX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FviruJRX.png&h=61899741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成功例子：Somi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/A9ZcN5o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FA9ZcN5o.jpg&h=3d1af3a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n投票方法：<br />\n1）入呢個網，揀你想投嘅練習生，禁佢地個大頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://101maboy.com/m101.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F101maboy.com%2Fm101.php&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=6b15da9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://101maboy.com/m101.php</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/4mOcmNw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4mOcmNw.png&h=0a012edf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2）然後碌落去會見到呢個，禁呢個<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/5Fs5f0L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5Fs5f0L.png&h=5ab7fb86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3）會彈出呢個畫面，禁多次藍色就得㗎喇<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/chOZvFT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FchOZvFT.png&h=15a034ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n＊如果第一次投會叫你用SNS登入 用Facebook 登入就OK<br />\n<br />\n4）因為每日只可以投一次（記住香港時間23:00就已經係韓國嘅00:00 即係第2日）<br />\n<strong>每日只可以投每個練習生一次</strong><br />\n所以投多過一次就會叫你收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/N7F8FYg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FN7F8FYg.png&h=c41d9013&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66602971c6649caefb71fcd039e528af1aedc52a","tid":202551,"uid":1776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1fbcfada67ca77ee45533790f00bd0b3c8e4d94","tid":202551,"uid":50242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:56:35.000Z","msg":"投飄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb05bb1cc82ce72982cf4d825efa69fbe7966d7c","tid":202551,"uid":46133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:56:45.000Z","msg":"仲要開兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ce6cb8b80b961541f93747e865e7d70d3b40cf","tid":202551,"uid":46133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:57:08.000Z","msg":"31呀彬巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d985e2f002628a00bce371e64e048d0cbe6c5da8","tid":202551,"uid":27504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:57:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲要開兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2a66d718f35353a4274c5e52ed2895f4dbfebd","tid":202551,"uid":104502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:57:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲要開兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=